You want me to leave?

56
00:05:19,752 --> 00:05:21,151
不是
No.

57
00:05:24,257 --> 00:05:28,489
-不是 -很好，因为我不打算走
- No. - Good, because I'm not.

58
00:05:35,768 --> 00:05:37,360
拿去吧
Here you go.

59
