115
00:09:00,940 --> 00:09:02,908
我们半价的东西都在后面
our half price stuff's in the back.

116
00:09:03,075 --> 00:09:06,909
-我要找一个特别的东西 -好
- I'm looking for something very specific. - Okay.

117
00:09:11,250 --> 00:09:13,115
就是这个
This is it.

118
00:09:13,953 --> 00:09:17,411
-我就是需要这个 -太好了
- This is exactly what I need. - Great.

119
00:09:19,625 --> 00:09:22,788
我们今天就差这么一点 就这么一点点
We were just inches away today. Inches.

120
00:09:22,962 --> 00:09:24,156
