- Put them up in my office, on the walls. - What are these?

122
00:09:27,033 --> 00:09:30,093
里面有资讯 是关于史柯菲准备的集合地点
In there is information regarding a rendezvous that scofield set up.

123
00:09:30,269 --> 00:09:31,998
我们今天就要破解密码 蓝恩
We're gonna crack that code today. Lang!

124
00:09:32,171 --> 00:09:35,334
富兰克林告诉老婆 今天要在彩虹厅见面
Today's the day Franklin told his wife he'll meet her at the Rainbow Room.

125
00:09:35,508 --> 00:09:37,840
-没错 -错了，今天是富兰克林被逮捕的日子
- Right. - Wrong. Today Franklin's going down.

126
00:09:38,010 --> 00:09:40,444
-准备好了吗？ -一切已经准备就绪
- Are you ready? - Everything's arranged.

127
00:09:45,484 --> 00:09:48,214
（伊利诺州，芝加哥）

128
00:10:00,232 --> 00:10:01,927
-都在这里了吗？ -对
- It's all here? - Yeah.

129
00:10:05,571 --> 00:10:07,630
雷，我们走
Yo, Ray, let's go.

130
00:10:08,441 --> 00:10:10,466
崔，你好吗？
Hey, yo, Trey. What's up, nigga?

131
00:10:11,978 --> 00:10:15,345
-我就知道不是你 -我可不是鬼
- I know that ain't you. - It ain't a ghost, man.

132
00:10:15,648 --> 00:10:16,876
你还好吗？
You holding up all right?

133
00:10:17,049 --> 00:10:20,212
我搭了很久的公车 才抵达芝加哥
Just catching a whole bunch of buses just to get here to Chi-Town, man.

134
00:10:20,386 --> 00:10:22,718
你觉得我的感觉会好吗？
How you think I'm supposed to feel?

135
00:10:23,222 --> 00:10:25,452
克里斯、杰，你们好吗？
Chris, Jay. What's up, Flam?

136
00:10:25,625 --> 00:10:27,149
你看起来瘦了，老哥
You look like you lost a few, bro.

137
00:10:27,326 --> 00:10:29,817
-我吃减肥餐 -是这样吗？
- Slim-Fast, baby. - Is that what it is?

138
00:10:29,996 --> 00:10:33,261
调查局一直盯着你的老婆 到你家监视
Feds been in your old lady's business, no joke. Up in your crib.

139
00:10:33,432 --> 00:10:35,525
