- Following her around. - Yeah, I know, man.

140
00:10:35,701 --> 00:10:36,895
我知道你爱凯西
Yo, I know you love Kacee.

141
00:10:37,069 --> 00:10:39,902
可是你来这里 我不知道是不是好主意
I don't know if it's a good idea for you to come around here.

142
00:10:40,072 --> 00:10:41,061
你是通缉犯
You're a wanted man.

143
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,969
我被通缉是因为我守口如瓶
I'm wanted because I kept my mouth shut.

144
00:10:43,142 --> 00:10:44,700
让你们不必坐牢
And I kept you out of Fox River.

145
00:10:44,877 --> 00:10:47,368
百元钞票 我们了解，我们欠你人情
C-Man, we feel that. And we owe you one.

146
00:10:48,381 --> 00:10:51,248
很好 我现在要你们还我人情债
Good, because I'm collecting right now.

147
00:10:51,917 --> 00:10:53,282
我妻子今天在等我
My wife is waiting for me...

148
00:10:53,452 --> 00:10:56,421
今天我一定要带家人离开芝加哥 懂了吗？
...and I am not leaving Chi-town without my family, you understand?

149
00:10:56,589 --> 00:11:00,252
你们全都得帮我 我们走吧！
Now, you all are gonna help me. Let's roll out.

150
00:11:13,773 --> 00:11:15,331
你要上哪去？
Where you going?

151
00:11:17,943 --> 00:11:19,934
载女儿去上学
To take my kid to school.

152
00:11:20,112 --> 00:11:21,841
我知道彩虹厅的事
I know about the Rainbow Room.

153
00:11:22,014 --> 00:11:24,915
-我不懂你的意思 -我们窃听你的电话
- I don't know what you're talking about. - Phone lines are tapped.

154
00:11:25,084 --> 00:11:27,382
我们听到你和丈夫的 完整对话内容
We heard your entire conversation with your husband.

155
00:11:27,553 --> 00:11:30,317
既然你和蒂蒂 没有买去纽约的机票
Since you and Dede aren't booked on any flights to New York...

156
00:11:30,489 --> 00:11:33,322
别说彩虹厅是曼哈顿的餐厅
...don't tell me the Rainbow Room is a restaurant in Manhattan.

157
00:11:33,492 --> 00:11:35,392
你可以告诉我 和丈夫的见面地点
Tell me where you're meeting your husband.

158
00:11:35,561 --> 00:11:38,997
不然我可以 在你女儿面前逮捕你
Or I can arrest you. Right in front of your daughter.

159
00:11:39,999 --> 00:11:43,093
你去死吧，我没有做错事
You go to hell. I haven't done anything wrong.

160
00:11:45,337 --> 00:11:48,067
你和一名逃犯谈到 今天要和他见面
You spoke with an escaped felon about meeting him today.

161
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:51,004
这足够控告你教唆犯罪
You've done enough to be charged with attempt to aid and abet.

162
00:11:51,177 --> 00:11:53,873
拜托，听我说
Please, okay. Listen to me.

163
00:11:54,046 --> 00:11:55,946
我打一通电话 儿童福利局就会来
One phone call and Child Welfare is here.

164
00:11:56,115 --> 00:11:58,606
你去坐牢 蒂蒂会被送去寄养家庭
You're going to County, Dede will be in foster care.

165
00:11:58,784 --> 00:11:59,773
-不 -别担心
- No. - Don't worry.

166
00:11:59,952 --> 00:12:03,251
我听说寄养家庭都是好人家
I hear the families in the foster system are topnotch.

